"Ona je rekla* da će doći za pola sata." (She said she would come in half an hour.)
"Rekla* sam da ću se javiti." (I said I would call.)
"Šta je rekla*?" (What did she say?)
"Reklo* se da će biti loše vreme." (It was said that the weather would be bad.)
"Rekli* smo da nećemo otići." (We said we wouldn't go.)